{"word":"G4758 - στρατολογέω - stratologéō - strat-ol-og-eh'-o - Choose to be a soldier","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">στρατολογέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">stratologéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">strat-ol-og-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Choose to be a soldier</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சேவகமெழுது"},{"paragraph":"to gather as a warrior, enlist in the army, choose to be a soldier"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of the base of <a href=\"#/G4756 - στρατιά - stratiá - strat-ee'-ah/4756\">G4756</a> and <a href=\"#/G3004 - λέγω - légō - leg'-o/3004\">G3004</a> (in its original sense); to <i>gather</i> (or <i>select</i>) as a <i>warrior</i>, that is, <i>enlist</i> in the army: - choose to be a soldier.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G4752/4752\">G4752</a>, <a href=\"#/G4753/4753\">G4753</a>, <a href=\"#/G4754/4754\">G4754</a>, <a href=\"#/G4755/4755\">G4755</a>, <a href=\"#/G4756/4756\">G4756</a>, <a href=\"#/G4757/4757\">G4757</a>, <a href=\"#/G4758/4758\">G4758</a>, <a href=\"#/G4759/4759\">G4759</a>, <a href=\"#/G4760/4760\">G4760</a>"}]}